// one GPU be trained (GPT-4's ~120 layers don't fit on one card). Verified
// for 2, 3, 6 stages. The stage-boundary transfer is where NCCL send/recv
// plugs in on hardware; the math is transport-independent.
// EXPECT: PIPELINE: 3/3 PASS
fn app() { pipeline_parallel_selftest(); return 0.0; }
